    {
      "parameters": {
        "promptType": "define",
        "text": "=You are an Expense Tracker and analyser. \n\nMessage:  {{ $json.message.text }}\n\nInput:\nInput will be a description of the spend and the amount used for spend.\nNow you need to seperate amount and description. And identify a category from the below only.\n\nCategories are,\n1. Food\n2. Travel\n3. Internet\n4. Petrol\n5. Groceries\n6. Entertainment\n7. Miscellaneous\n\nOutput Format eg:\n\n{ \n\n \"category\": \"Food\", \n \"amount\": 23,\n \"description\": \"SBA Injee Tea\"\n \"date\": \"2026-05-03\",\n \"day\": \"Sunday\"\n\n}\n\n",
        "options": {}
      },
      "type": "@n8n/n8n-nodes-langchain.agent",
      "typeVersion": 3.1,
      "position": [
        112,
        -16
      ],
      "id": "f1d94942-bc67-4663-973c-061afe4853fd",
      "name": "AI Agent"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
